# Important Interview Point

For:

```java id="mjlwm0"
n/2  -> maximum 1 majority element
n/3  -> maximum 2 majority elements
n/k  -> maximum (k-1) majority elements
```

This is the extension of the Boyer-Moore Voting Algorithm.
